arStrings.szText: "Thank you, truly. But don't you need time to rest and heal?"
Ah, friend. Your heart is in a good place. But you wield it with the subtlety of a hammer.
This wound, this... loss, is mine. Mine to carry, mine to tend. I will grieve it with my family in the privacy of my home.
For now, let’s stay focused on Neyrelle. That’s where the Pale Hand comes in. We can help fight your fight.
My friends from those days are scattered across Sanctuary. I want you to find them, bring them here. It may take some convincing... but I’m sure you can manage.
